dit logging, destructive actions, and access controls before phase completion.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(101,14,NULL,NULL,'Core Identity','Define Guild CMS versioning, schema versioning, API versioning, and platform identity.','planned',0,10,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(102,14,NULL,NULL,'Service Container','Create a foundation for shared services and dependency management.','planned',0,20,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(103,14,NULL,NULL,'Security Header Service','Refactor security headers/CSP into a platform service.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(104,14,NULL,NULL,'Core Security Review','Review core services, bootstrap, configuration, error handling, and platform assumptions before phase completion.','planned',0,40,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(105,15,NULL,NULL,'Site Registry','Manage multiple sites/sections through a consistent CMS registry.','planned',0,10,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(106,15,NULL,NULL,'Site Settings','Move site identity, URLs, assets, navigation, and feature toggles into managed settings.','planned',0,20,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(107,15,NULL,NULL,'Site Management Security Review','Review per-site isolation, permissions, settings validation, and access control before phase completion.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(108,16,NULL,NULL,'Theme Manifest','Define theme metadata, assets, compatibility, parent/child relationships, and settings.','planned',0,10,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(109,16,NULL,NULL,'Theme Asset Pipeline','Load theme CSS/JS/assets consistently and safely.','planned',0,20,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(110,16,NULL,NULL,'Theme Security Review','Review template escaping, asset loading, CSP compatibility, and upload/install behavior before phase completion.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(111,17,NULL,NULL,'Marketplace Model','Define how plugins are listed, discovered, installed, and updated.','planned',0,10,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(112,17,NULL,NULL,'Package Validation','Define validation and trust checks for plugin packages.','planned',0,20,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(113,17,NULL,NULL,'Marketplace Security Review','Review package authenticity, upload/install controls, dependency handling, and trust boundaries before phase completion.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(114,18,NULL,NULL,'Platform-Wide Security Audit','Review headers, CSP, sessions, cookies, CSRF, uploads, filesystem, installer, plugins, themes, admin, and public surfaces.','planned',0,10,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(115,18,NULL,NULL,'Release Readiness Review','Validate documentation, installer, upgrade path, public site, packaging, versioning, and release candidate readiness.','planned',0,20,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(116,18,NULL,NULL,'Release Candidate Sign-Off','Confirm all critical findings are resolved and approve the release candidate for public release.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(117,19,NULL,NULL,'Public Package Release','Publish the initial public Guild CMS release package.','planned',0,10,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(118,19,NULL,NULL,'Public Documentation','Publish installation, configuration, upgrade, and security documentation.','planned',0,20,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(119,19,NULL,NULL,'Announcement','Announce the public release after release readiness sign-off.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-29 15:07:55',NULL,1),(120,8,NULL,NULL,'Content Security Policy Audit','Inventory asset sources and deploy Content-Security-Policy-Report-Only.','complete',100,40,'2026-06-29 16:11:25',NULL,1),(121,8,NULL,NULL,'Filesystem & Permissions Audit','Review writable paths and correct legacy 777 directory/file permissions.','complete',100,60,'2026-06-29 16:11:25',NULL,1),(122,8,NULL,NULL,'Gallery Upload Hardening','Improve Gallery upload validation, MIME checking, pre-move validation, and upload-directory execution protection.','complete',100,70,'2026-06-29 16:11:25',NULL,1),(123,11,NULL,NULL,'Engineering Library','Introduce the Guild CMS Engineering Library as the canonical public source for engineering documentation.','complete',100,10,'2026-06-29 19:17:10','2026-06-30 11:34:02',1),(124,11,NULL,NULL,'Engineering Governance','Establish architecture standards, engineering principles, coding standards, security standards, and ADR preparation.','complete',100,20,'2026-06-29 19:17:10','2026-06-30 11:34:02',1),(125,11,NULL,NULL,'Development Center Realignment','Update the Development Center to reflect the revised roadmap and the start of Phase 4.3.','complete',100,30,'2026-06-29 19:17:10',NULL,1),(126,11,NULL,NULL,'Engineering Publications','Publish GCMS-ENG-000 through GCMS-ENG-010 as Engineering Library Volume I.','complete',100,431,'2026-06-30 11:34:02',NULL,1),(127,11,NULL,NULL,'Architecture Decision Records','Establish ADR structure, lifecycle, numbering, and initial foundational architecture decisions.','complete',100,432,'2026-06-30 11:34:02',NULL,1),(128,11,NULL,NULL,'Engineering Workflow','Establish architecture discussion, implementation, security review, public site, and release package workflow.','complete',100,433,'2026-06-30 11:34:02',NULL,1),(129,12,NULL,NULL,'Installer Bootstrap Framework','Create the first installer architecture and bootstrap workflow foundation.','complete',100,448,'2026-06-30 11:34:02','2026-07-01 23:26:37',1),(130,12,NULL,'4.4.0-1','Installation Architecture','Define installer boundaries, bootstrap stage model, devsite installable-product role, package sequence, and security expectations.','complete',100,10,'2026-06-30 12:11:21','2026-06-30 13:54:12',1),(131,22,NULL,'4.5.0-1','Data Normalization Planning','Define the scope, conventions, and audit plan for Guild CMS data normalization and governance.','planned',0,10,'2026-06-30 13:10:51','2026-06-30 13:10:51',1),(132,22,NULL,'4.5.0-2','Roadmap Data Normalization','Normalize roadmap phase and item data, including sort order, status, progress, public visibility, and duplicate/conflicting rows.','planned',0,20,'2026-06-30 13:10:51','2026-06-30 13:10:51',1),(133,22,NULL,'4.5.0-3','Publication and Release Data Governance','Normalize publication tracking, release records, changelog patterns, timeline entries, and journal conventions.','planned',0,30,'2026-06-30 13:10:51','2026-06-30 13:10:51',1),(134,22,NULL,'4.5.0-4','SQL Migration Governance','Establish database migration standards, idempotency rules, schema review practices, and shared SQL delivery conventions.','planned',0,40,'2026-06-30 13:10:51','2026-06-30 13:10:51',1),(141,12,NULL,'4.4.0-2','Installer Framework','Create the initial installer framework skeleton inside devsite and establish the separation between installable product code and reference/documentation sites.','complete',100,20,'2026-06-30 13:54:12','2026-06-30 13:54:12',1),(142,12,NULL,'GCMS-ENG-011','GCMS-ENG-011 – User Experience & Educational Design Principles','Publish the Engineering Library guidance that defines user-facing experience principles: explain before asking, teach rather than assume, build confidence, and provide recovery-oriented errors.','complete',100,25,'2026-06-30 13:54:12','2026-06-30 14:53:01',1),(144,12,NULL,'4.4.0-4','Product Separation Audit','Audit and remove hardcoded TheRegs assumptions from the installable product tree so Guild CMS can become a clean distributable CMS.','planned',0,40,'2026-06-30 13:54:12','2026-06-30 13:54:12',1),(145,12,NULL,'4.4.0-5','System Readiness Check','Implement the first testable installer validation step with required server checks, recommended feature checks, clear explanations, corrective guidance, and safe recheck behavior.','complete',100,50,'2026-06-30 13:54:12','2026-06-30 15:38:18',1),(146,12,NULL,'4.4.0-8','Installer Environment Detection & Platform Intelligence','Detect operating system, distribution version, package manager family, web server, PHP runtime, PHP extensions, database drivers, filesystem readiness, effective PHP user/group, document root, HTTPS status, SELinux, and AppArmor so later installer steps can provide educational platform-aware guidance.','complete',100,48,'2026-06-30 13:54:12','2026-06-30 18:28:22',1),(147,12,NULL,'first-installer','First Installer Experience','Introduce setup detection, a welcoming unconfigured-site page, installer progress navigation, required system readiness checks, recommended feature checks, save/cancel controls, and the first educational installer workflow in devsite.','complete',100,35,'2026-06-30 15:16:23','2026-06-30 15:16:23',1),(148,12,NULL,'GCMS-ENG-012','GCMS-ENG-012 - Installer Testing & Certification Framework','Defines installer testing philosophy, runtime support policy, certification environments, base and perfect expectations, failure and recovery tests, UX validation, security checks, and release certification standards.','complete',100,36,'2026-06-30 16:52:08',NULL,1),(149,12,NULL,'GCMS-ENG-013','GCMS-ENG-013 - Guild CMS Development & Release Standard','Defines the official Guild CMS package workflow, repository layout, release documentation, SQL migration rules, roadmap semantics, validation gates, package manifests, and Git baseline policy.','complete',100,37,'2026-06-30 17:26:03',NULL,1),(150,12,NULL,NULL,'Installer Certification Milestone 1 - Foundation Platforms','Publish certification reports for Rocky Linux 9.8 with Virtualmin, Rocky Linux 9.8 Minimal, AlmaLinux 9.8 Minimal, Ubuntu 24 Minimal, and Debian 12 Minimal using the standardized Installer Certification Report format.','complete',100,499,'2026-07-01 23:26:37',NULL,1),(151,12,NULL,NULL,'Configuration Generation','Collect database, site, path, and environment values and generate safe configuration output with review-friendly explanations.','archived',0,451,'2026-07-01 23:26:37','2026-07-01 23:53:30',0),(152,12,NULL,NULL,'Database Initialization','Create and seed the initial Guild CMS schema required for a new installation.','planned',0,453,'2026-07-01 23:26:37','2026-07-01 23:53:30',1),(153,12,NULL,NULL,'Administrator Account Creation','Create the first administrator account or validate the selected authentication provider during installation.','planned',0,454,'2026-07-01 23:26:37','2026-07-01 23:53:30',1),(154,12,NULL,NULL,'First-Run Site Configuration','Initialize site identity, base settings, default content, and initial public/admin runtime state.','planned',0,455,'2026-07-01 23:26:37','2026-07-01 23:53:30',1),(155,12,NULL,NULL,'Installation Locking and Recovery','Lock completed installations, prevent unsafe re-runs, and document recovery or reinstall workflows.','planned',0,460,'2026-07-01 23:26:37','2026-07-01 23:53:30',1);
